<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>BlueRoots | Unified Text, Email, and Voice Campaigns</title>
  <meta name="description" content="BlueRoots brings text, email, and voice into one clear communications platform with shared contacts, faster campaign setup, and cleaner reporting.">
  <meta name="author" content="BlueRoots">
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://blueroots.io/">
  <meta property="og:title" content="BlueRoots | Unified Text, Email, and Voice Campaigns">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Run text, email, and voice campaigns from one clear platform with shared contacts, cleaner workflows, and live reporting.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://blueroots.io/">
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="BlueRoots">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="BlueRoots | Unified Text, Email, and Voice Campaigns">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Run text, email, and voice campaigns from one clear platform with shared contacts, cleaner workflows, and live reporting.">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #121b2a;
      --muted: #5b6f86;
      --navy: #17335d;
      --blue: #4e8fc7;
      --cyan: #6fd0d6;
      --peach: #e3a065;
      --green: #4e9b72;
      --paper: #eef2f7;
      --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      --line: rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.12);
      --shadow: 0 24px 56px rgba(23, 51, 93, 0.14);
      --r-xl: 32px;
      --r-lg: 24px;
      --r-md: 18px;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 8%, rgba(111, 208, 214, 0.2), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 90% 14%, rgba(227, 160, 101, 0.18), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f4f7fb 0%, #e9eff6 100%);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 44px 44px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35), transparent 75%);
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .wrap { width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px)); max-width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      padding: 16px 0;
      background: rgba(238, 242, 247, 0.76);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.08);
    }
    .topbar-inner, .hero-grid, .proof-grid, .service-grid, .workflow-grid, .pricing, .cta-shell, .footer {
      display: grid;
    }
    .topbar-inner {
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--navy), #264b83);
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(23, 51, 93, 0.2);
    }
    .brand-copy small, .eyebrow, .kicker, .mini, .card-label {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      font-size: 11px;
    }
    .brand-copy small { display: block; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .brand-copy strong { font-size: 18px; }
    .nav { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 24px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }
    .nav a:hover, .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--navy); }
    .actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 13px 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 180ms ease;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--navy); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(23, 51, 93, 0.18); }
    .btn-secondary { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66); border-color: rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.1); }

    .hero { padding: 34px 0 54px; }
    .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.06fr 0.94fr; gap: 22px; align-items: center; }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--navy);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.56);
      border: 1px solid rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.08);
    }
    .eyebrow::before {
      content: "";
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--cyan);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(111, 208, 214, 0.16);
    }
    h1, h2, h3, .stat strong, .price, .channel-name, .panel-number {
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(32px, 4.8vw, 50px); line-height: 1.04; margin: 0 0 14px; max-width: 12ch; }
    .hero-copy p { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 0 18px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.62; }
    .hero-row, .hero-note { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
    .hero-row { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .hero-note { gap: 18px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }
    .hero-note span::before {
      content: "";
      display: inline-block;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      margin-right: 9px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--peach);
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .hero-panel, .proof-card, .service-card, .workflow-card, .feature-card, .cta-shell, .footer {
      min-width: 0;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }
    .hero-panel {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: var(--r-xl);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(23, 51, 93, 0.11);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92), rgba(242, 247, 252, 0.88));
    }
    .hero-panel::before, .hero-panel::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(12px);
    }
    .hero-panel::before { width: 220px; height: 220px; right: -70px; top: -76px; background: rgba(111, 208, 214, 0.18); }
    .hero-panel::after { width: 170px; height: 170px; left: -70px; bottom: -68px; background: rgba(78, 143, 199, 0.12); }
    .mini { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 12px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .platform-panel { position: relative; z-index: 1; display: grid; gap: 14px; }
    .panel-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .panel-dots { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
    .panel-dots span { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.18); }
    .panel-dots span:first-child { background: rgba(227, 160, 101, 0.9); }
    .panel-dots span:nth-child(2) { background: rgba(111, 208, 214, 0.9); }
    .panel-status {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(78, 155, 114, 0.14);
      color: #2d6d4c;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .panel-canvas {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.74);
      border: 1px solid rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.08);
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .command-card {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), #2c5d96);
    }
    .command-card strong { display: block; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .command-card span { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); font-size: 12px; }
    .channel-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 10px; }
    .channel-card {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.045);
      border: 1px solid rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.08);
    }
    .channel-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 7px 11px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .channel-chip.sms { background: rgba(111, 208, 214, 0.18); color: #176975; }
    .channel-chip.email { background: rgba(227, 160, 101, 0.18); color: #8d5b21; }
    .channel-chip.voice { background: rgba(78, 155, 114, 0.16); color: #2d6d4c; }
    .channel-name { display: block; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .channel-card p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.48; font-size: 14px; }
    .panel-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 10px; }
    .panel-stat {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(24, 51, 93, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.08);
    }
    .panel-number { display: block; font-size: 21px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: var(--navy); }
    .panel-stat span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; }

    .section { padding: 22px 0 72px; }
    .proof-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-top: 14px; }
    .proof-card, .service-card, .workflow-card, .feature-card { border-radius: var(--r-lg); padding: 22px; box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(23, 51, 93, 0.06); }
    .card-label { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .proof-card strong { display: block; font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .proof-card p, .service-card p, .workflow-card p, .feature-card p, .section-copy, .footer-note, .cta-copy p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }
    .kicker { color: var(--navy); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .section-title { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 54px); line-height: 0.98; }
    .section-copy { max-width: 640px; }
    .tag {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(24, 51, 93, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.08);
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .service-grid, .pricing { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
    .service-card { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .service-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: -24px;
      right: -24px;
      width: 88px;
      height: 88px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(111, 208, 214, 0.12);
    }
    .service-icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(23, 51, 93, 0.12), rgba(227, 160, 101, 0.16));
      color: var(--navy);
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .workflow-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .workflow-card.navy { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #17335d, #102746); color: #fff; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); }
    .workflow-card.navy p, .workflow-card.navy .caption { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); }
    .metric-row { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 18px; }
    .metric { flex: 1 1 120px; padding: 14px; border-radius: 16px; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); }
    .metric strong { display: block; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .caption { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .rail { margin-top: 18px; background: rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.05); padding: 14px; border-radius: 18px; display: grid; gap: 12px; }
    .rail-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 14px; align-items: center; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.08); }
    .rail-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: 0; }
    .rail-item strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .chip { padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(78, 155, 114, 0.14); color: #2d6d4c; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; }

    .feature-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
    .feature-card { padding: 22px; }
    .feature-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(24, 51, 93, 0.07);
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .feature-list { display: grid; gap: 10px; margin-top: 16px; }
    .feature-item {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.045);
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .price { font-size: 42px; margin: 10px 0; }
    .price small { font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted); }
    .list { display: grid; gap: 10px; margin: 16px 0 0; padding: 0; list-style: none; }
    .list li { display: flex; gap: 10px; color: var(--muted); }
    .list li::before { content: "•"; color: var(--peach); font-weight: 700; }

    .cta { padding: 20px 0 80px; }
    .cta-shell {
      grid-template-columns: 1.08fr 0.92fr;
      gap: 22px;
      padding: 26px;
      border-radius: calc(var(--r-xl) + 4px);
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(18, 45, 80, 0.97), rgba(20, 33, 57, 0.98));
      box-shadow: 0 28px 70px rgba(16, 37, 63, 0.22);
    }
    .cta-copy p, .cta-band p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76); }
    .cta-band { padding: 18px; border-radius: 18px; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); display: grid; gap: 14px; }
    .cta-stat { padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
    .cta-stat:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: 0; }
    .cta-stat strong { font-size: 26px; }

    footer { padding: 0 0 40px; }
    .footer {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 22px 24px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.1);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(23, 51, 93, 0.06);
    }
    .footer-note, .footer-links, .footer-links a { color: var(--muted); }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 18px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-end; }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .hero-grid, .service-grid, .workflow-grid, .feature-grid, .pricing, .cta-shell { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .proof-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .topbar-inner { grid-template-columns: auto auto; }
      .nav { display: none; }
      .tag { white-space: normal; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .wrap { width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 20px)); }
      .topbar { padding: 12px 0; }
      .topbar-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .actions { width: 100%; }
      .actions .btn, .hero-row .btn { flex: 1 1 0; width: 100%; }
      .hero { padding: 20px 0 42px; }
      .hero-grid { gap: 22px; }
      h1 { max-width: none; font-size: clamp(30px, 9vw, 40px); line-height: 1.04; }
      .hero-copy p { font-size: 15px; }
      .hero-panel { padding: 16px; }
      .channel-grid, .panel-stats, .proof-grid, .service-grid, .feature-grid, .pricing, .footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .section { padding: 14px 0 54px; }
      .section-head { align-items: start; gap: 14px; }
      .tag { width: 100%; }
      .cta-shell, .footer { padding: 18px; }
      .footer-links { justify-content: flex-start; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="wrap topbar-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="https://blueroots.io">
        <span class="brand-mark">B</span>
        <span class="brand-copy">
          <small>BlueRoots</small>
          <strong>Platform</strong>
        </span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#workflow">Workflow</a>
        <a href="#platform">Platform</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Plans</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://blueroots.io/login">Sign in</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://blueroots.io/register">Start free</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="wrap hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <div class="eyebrow">Unified communication with cleaner control</div>
          <h1>Run text, email, and voice campaigns from one clear BlueRoots workspace.</h1>
          <p>
            BlueRoots brings messaging, calling, shared contacts, and live reporting into one platform so your team can move faster without juggling disconnected tools.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://blueroots.io/register">Create your account</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#services">See the services</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-note">
            <span>Shared contacts across every channel</span>
            <span>Faster campaign setup and launch</span>
            <span>Cleaner reporting and account control</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-panel">
          <div class="mini">Unified campaign preview</div>
          <div class="platform-panel">
            <div class="panel-head">
              <div class="panel-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
              <div class="panel-status">Platform ready</div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel-canvas">
              <div class="command-card">
                <strong>Multi-channel launch board</strong>
                <span>Audience selected • channels aligned • reporting live</span>
              </div>

              <div class="channel-grid">
                <div class="channel-card">
                  <div class="channel-chip sms">Text</div>
                  <span class="channel-name">SMS campaigns</span>
                  <p>Send reminders, updates, and direct asks from the same contact base.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="channel-card">
                  <div class="channel-chip email">Email</div>
                  <span class="channel-name">Email sends</span>
                  <p>Build cleaner email campaigns with stronger structure and reporting.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="channel-card">
                  <div class="channel-chip voice">Voice</div>
                  <span class="channel-name">Voice outreach</span>
                  <p>Run live calls, broadcasts, and voicemail workflows with shared context.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="panel-stats">
                <div class="panel-stat"><span class="panel-number">3</span><span>services managed from one dashboard and account context</span></div>
                <div class="panel-stat"><span class="panel-number">1</span><span>shared contact system across text, email, and voice</span></div>
                <div class="panel-stat"><span class="panel-number">Live</span><span>reporting and performance visibility after launch</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap proof-grid">
        <div class="proof-card"><div class="card-label">Less switching</div><strong>One platform</strong><p>Keep messaging, calling, account access, and contact management in one operational system.</p></div>
        <div class="proof-card"><div class="card-label">Better coordination</div><strong>Shared contacts</strong><p>Use the same audience model across every service without rebuilding lists channel by channel.</p></div>
        <div class="proof-card"><div class="card-label">Cleaner execution</div><strong>Faster launches</strong><p>Move from planning to live sends more quickly with aligned tools and simpler workflows.</p></div>
        <div class="proof-card"><div class="card-label">Clearer visibility</div><strong>Live reporting</strong><p>Watch delivery, engagement, and channel performance without bouncing through separate tools.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="services">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <div class="kicker">Services</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Three communication channels, one operating layer.</h2>
            <p class="section-copy">Each service is focused on its own workflow, but they all stay tied together through the same account, contacts, and platform context.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tag">Text, email, and voice under one roof</div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-grid">
          <article class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">T</div>
            <h3>Text</h3>
            <p>Launch SMS campaigns, reminders, alerts, and short-form outreach with contact groups that stay synced with the rest of BlueRoots.</p>
            <div class="hero-row" style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0;"><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://text.blueroots.io">Open Text</a></div>
          </article>
          <article class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">E</div>
            <h3>Email</h3>
            <p>Build structured email campaigns with stronger layout control, segmentation, and deliverability-aware reporting.</p>
            <div class="hero-row" style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0;"><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://email.blueroots.io">Open Email</a></div>
          </article>
          <article class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">V</div>
            <h3>Voice</h3>
            <p>Run individual calls, broadcasts, and voicemail campaigns while keeping voice outreach tied to the same contact system.</p>
            <div class="hero-row" style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0;"><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://voice.blueroots.io">Open Voice</a></div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
